column2: Couldn't reach the charging dock, remove any obstacles, and clean the dock's transmission area.
Cannot reach the dock, please remove any obstacles!

An internal error occurred. Reboot the system.
Error 1, Turn the laser unit, and check that it is not jammed, or blocked.
Error 2, Clean and lightly tap the bumper.
Error 3, Move the main unit to a new location, and restart.
Error 4, Clean cliff sensors. Move the main unit away from any drops, then restart.
Error 5, Remove and clean the main brush and brush bearing.
Error 6, Remove and clean the side brush.
Error 7, Check that wheels are not blocked, then move the main unit to a new location, and restart.
Error 8, Remove any obstacles around the main unit.
Error 9, Reinstall dustbin and filter.
Error 10, Check the filter.  If wet, use a dry one.  If dry, clean it, and try again.
Error 11, Strong magnetic field detected. Move the device away from barrier tape and restart.
Error 12, Battery level too low, recharge before use.
Error 13, Charging error.  Clean charging contacts, and try again.
Error 14, Battery error.
Error 15, Clean wall sensor.
Error 16, Place and start the main unit on a level floor.
Error 17, Side brush module error. Reset the main unit.
Error 18, Fan error. Reset the main unit.
Error 19, There is no current on the charging base. Check connection to a power supply.
Error 21, Height sensor has been pressed.  Move the main unit, and restart.
Error 22, Clean the recharge sensor on the main unit.
Error 23, Clean the transmission area on the charging dock.
Error 24, No-Go-Zone or barrier tape detected. Move the main unit away, and restart.
